ActAn Act to amend the Canada Business Corporations Act and to make consequential and related amendments to other Acts
SubjectOrder Fixing January 22, 2024 as the Day on Which Certain Provisions of An Act to amend the Canada Business Corporations Act and to make consequential and related amendments to other Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing January 22, 2024 as the day on which certain provisions of An Act to amend the Canada Business Corporations Act and to make consequential and related amendments to other Acts come into force in order to bring into force the legislative amendments to the CANADA BUSINESS CORPORATIONS ACT.
